data.description: Lovely  home in a gated community of Northshores with 5 bdr +3 bath. One of the bedrooms is located on a first floor. Brand new flooring and paint. New dishwasher and stove, Master bathroom boasts an amazing walk-in shower, two sinks. Main bedroom has a good size Balcony. Great room, pot shelves & soothing grey finishes compliment this home. close to shopping and freeway.
